  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Cymut X Mutrobo - The Last Cymut</u></h2>It's a thrilling action-strategy game that puts players in the role of Watfrog, the Last Cymut, on a quest to free his companions in Mutrobo territory. Face challenging enemies, imposing bosses and explore a world full of traps and secrets.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>History</u></h2>The Cymuts invaded the Mutrobos' territory in an attempt to defeat them, but were eventually defeated and almost all of them were imprisoned. Now, only Watfrog, the Last Cymut, remains, with the mission of finding and freeing the 11 imprisoned Cymuts, as well as the legendary Dracomut, whose power can be used when freeing him. However, being in Mutrobo territory means facing countless enemies, 6 challenging bosses and overcoming numerous traps and obstacles to reach your goal. Get ready for an epic journey filled with excitement and unimaginable dangers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Choose the phase</u></h2>There are 6 stages and 6 bosses, choose wisely and pay attention to the temperature.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/7ecf57ed0a4f443690814e3388c721a1.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/7ecf57ed0a4f443690814e3388c721a1.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/7ecf57ed0a4f443690814e3388c721a1.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Choose your Cymuts team</u></h2>You can select up to 4 Cymuts to play, after freeing all the Cymuts, you will have 12 options, choose wisely, each Cymut has its own attributes and pay attention to temperature resistance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/301150d2a15dcdbbd3c1fb83cbfeeed9.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/301150d2a15dcdbbd3c1fb83cbfeeed9.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/301150d2a15dcdbbd3c1fb83cbfeeed9.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Collect Enercoin</u></h2>Collect as many Enercoins as you can to free Cymuts and challenge bosses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/a84907c1527fd90ed5a6f5f7bd3d6a8e.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/a84907c1527fd90ed5a6f5f7bd3d6a8e.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/a84907c1527fd90ed5a6f5f7bd3d6a8e.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Freeing Cymut</u></h2>Find and free all trapped Cymuts and use them in battle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/fbaa048791e05463d7f95b7dfbe42e93.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/fbaa048791e05463d7f95b7dfbe42e93.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/fbaa048791e05463d7f95b7dfbe42e93.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Cymut Exchange</u></h2>Choose a team of up to 4 Cymuts to use in battle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/146bacb728cbfd13d91e3f2004553d1f.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/146bacb728cbfd13d91e3f2004553d1f.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/146bacb728cbfd13d91e3f2004553d1f.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Releasing Phase</u></h2>Find and release the 4 locked stages.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/d2aac4f5bc5d0d361219f607c80c91b6.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/d2aac4f5bc5d0d361219f607c80c91b6.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/d2aac4f5bc5d0d361219f607c80c91b6.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Special Ability</u></h2>Each Cymut has a Special Ability that needs to be used in a specific location.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/3034c23d8967e172f07c721e51575b14.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/3034c23d8967e172f07c721e51575b14.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/3034c23d8967e172f07c721e51575b14.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Find the boss</u></h2>In each stage there is a boss that you need to find and challenge.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/aebf73caf797e51e282cf29b95e2933b.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/aebf73caf797e51e282cf29b95e2933b.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/aebf73caf797e51e282cf29b95e2933b.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Defeat the bosses</u></h2>Defeat the bosses and get the Boomags, which are magical books needed to free the Legendary Dracomut.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/ede4703d7d332083d275237f6d3ea22e.poster.avif?t=1717084956\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/ede4703d7d332083d275237f6d3ea22e.webm?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836530/extras/ede4703d7d332083d275237f6d3ea22e.mp4?t=1717084956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
